sub_title: International Agribusiness | Food Security | Water-Food nexus
summary:
Policy officer at the Ministry of Agriculture, Nature and Food Quality. Working in the international agribusiness and food security team as a country coordinator of Ethiopia, South-Africa, Uganda and Rwanda. Besides that, I am thematic coordinator of the water/food nexus. 

Global Business & Sustainability graduate from the Rotterdam School of Management with a specialization in Cross-sector partnerships and Global Value Chains for local development. Successful history with building unconventional stakeholder networks, social impact consulting and research on inclusive business networks for sustainable development.
